properties.Name: LifeInsuranceExclusionType
properties.Description:
Most life insurance policies contain restrictions that exclude from coverage certain types of risks.

An exclusion for an insurance policy under which benefits or claims would in some way be restricted.

Most life insurance policies contain restrictions that exclude from coverage certain types of risks.

Ex:
- Skydiving
- Auto Racing
- War
- Aviation
- Commission of a Felony
- Suicide
- Hazardous occupation or hobby
